#!new # vim:syntax=sh:tw=72

# REQUIREMENTS & DEFAULTS
--default VERS=0.0
--default AUTHOR=David C Black
--default EMAIL=dcblack@mac.com

# BRIEF
#! Creates simple Rust project

=pod

=head1 NAME

B<rust-project template> - Creates a simple Rust project

=head1 SYNOPSIS

B<new> rust-project I<OPTIONS> {:I<NAME>:}

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Creates a basic directory to build a simple SystemC project.

    NAME/
    ├── .gitattributes
    ├── .gitignore
    ├── ARCHIVE
    │   └── README.md
    ├── dev-tools
    │   ├── make-help.py
    │   └── README.md
    ├── GNUmakefile
    ├── NOTES
    │   └── README.md
    ├── README.md
    └── setup.profile

=head1 PARAMETERS

=over

=item AUTHOR

=item COMPANY

=item EMAIL

=item VERS

Version number #.# (defaults to 0.0)

=back

=head1 REQUIREMENTS

Rust cargo new needs to be executed.

=head1 AUTHOR

David C Black <dcblack@mac.com>

